tourBios.curYrHigh: Easily qualified for the PGA TOUR China Series' season, with a T4 finish at the Mainland China Qualifying Tournament in early March at Wolong Lake GC in Liuzhou.
tourBios.carHigh: 2014: Played a full slate of PGA TOUR China Series' events but only made two cuts—at the Buick Open (T58) and the Tour Championship presented by CTS Tycoon (T53).

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was T53rd in 2014 at the Tour Championship presented by CTS Tycoon.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T11th in Victory Leaders on the PGA Tour China Series.
